profile:
GTA Custom Homes & Renovations Since 2002.

Turn to Jon Marcus Homes and Restorations for residential construction services in Bradford, Newmarket and throughout the GTA. 

Our owner has worked in the industry since 1992 and started our independently owned and operated business in 2002. What this means for you is fast, efficient and dependable workmanship on jobs of all types. In fact, our new homes all come with a 7-year warranty.

Jon Marcus Homes and Restorations will get your job done properly and quickly. Over the years, we've seen and overcome all types of challenges and there is nothing that will deter us from achieving the exceptional final results you deserve.

We look forward to discussing the details of your job! Give us a call to set up a consultation.
